caption: Adorable little gem on Grand Street! The food is delicious and there’s a fairly large variety to choose from. The prices are more than reasonable. What makes this place even better is the fact they’ve worked with the community to feed those who are in need on the holidays. It’s special and shows who they are. TAKE MY MONEY AND FEED MY FACE!  (I took one star away because I wish their rice had just a bit more seasoning.)
